title: Touching Me, Touching You
description: Buckle up, Deep Divers, because June and Jessica are on their own again and like always, it will be a wild ride! First, they share how deeply they are touched by the amazing fan feedback, how a friend is reaching out for connection and Jessica's need to touch literally everyone. Then, they dig into why joy always seems to be followed by crushing anxiety, why disassociating gets a bad name and discover why Jessica is TJ Maxx, and June is Target. We want to know which one you are and why!
author: thedeepdive@earwolf.com (Earwolf & Jessica St. Clair, June Diane Rapheal)
